 [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his second Olympics\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"his scepticism\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"golf's place\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sport made its comeback to the Olympics only six years ago after a century in the shadows.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sport\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"its comeback\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"a century\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"the shadows\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back in 2016, amidst the Zika scare in Brazil, McIlroy opted out of the Rio Games along with several top players and once remarked before the Olympics comeback: \\\"I think I will be remembered for my major championships.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9888927506050059, \"rank\": 0.010932581876364658, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Zika scare\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rio Games\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"several top players\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics comeback\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"my major championships\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So all I have dreamed of from a little kid is winning majors.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little kid\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"majors\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never dreamed of competing in the Olympics or winning an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So in my mind, a major will always be more important.\\\"\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, after a long 10-year wait for another major title, the Team Ireland star suggests that winning an Olympic medal would now rank as a significant milestone in his career.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.3541938431774015e-19, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long 10-year wait\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"another major title\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant milestone\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a candid admission, the former Open champion highlighted the impact of such an achievement: \\\"It would be the achievement, certainly of the year,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases